3:53.000Z","msg":"啤酒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"至於啤酒，有利尿、促進胃液分泌、緩解緊張作用。喝啤酒多會選擇冷飲，喝下去是會覺得有點涼快，但是這種和中醫的清熱完全不同。酒一般都是性溫，而啤酒偏向濕熱，脾胃功能不好應盡量少飲，加上啤酒利尿，不能清積熱，長期飲用過多啤酒更會引致肝硬化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1961853/%E6%89%93%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%E6%B8%85%E7%86%B1%E6%B0%A3%E6%9C%89%E7%A6%81%E5%BF%8C%20%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E9%86%AB%EF%BC%9A%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%B8%85%E7%A9%8D%E7%86%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1961853%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%2588%2590%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25BF%258C%2520%2520%2520%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2586%25AB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2595%25A4%25E9%2585%2592%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25A9%258D%25E7%2586%25B1&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=ab7be349\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1961853/%E6%89%93%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%E6%B8%85%E7%86%B1%E6%B0%A3%E6%9C%89%E7%A6%81%E5%BF%8C%20%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E9%86%AB%EF%BC%9A%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%B8%85%E7%A9%8D%E7%86%B1</a>"},{"pid":"bc12ca01aba5562faf01f4dca96e5922ff4a00e2","tid":2112364,"uid":154106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"綠茶<br />\n花旗蔘"},{"pid":"c7d57acfda388f83951507c385872f0235d0c6c0","tid":2112364,"uid":11392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"綠豆"},{"pid":"3d497a066f82483255ada55ab283e769909fb5bf","tid":2112364,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"冰水"},{"pid":"cd3a0c67f392d689aa44ef6a4199f5d72ee7cc69","tid":2112364,"uid":105766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T00:26:52.000Z","msg":"Coconut water"}]}